CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Centuri is a strategic infrastructure services company that partners with regulated utilities to build and maintain the energy network that powers millions of homes and businesses across the U.S. and Canada. Guided by our values and unwavering commitment to serve as long term partners to customers and communities, Centuri's more than 12,000 employees enable our customers to safely and reliably deliver electricity and natural gas as well as achieve their goals for environmental sustainability. Centuri is a subsidiary of Southwest Gas Holdings, Inc.
